newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: China's Maoming refinery cuts output by 10-15 pct.
newsitem.headline: China's Maoming refinery cuts output by 10-15 pct.

text.p: China's state-owned Maoming Petrochemical Corp has cut runs at its 170,0000 barrels-per-day (bpd) refinery since mid July by 10-15 percent, sources familiar with the refinery said on Wednesday.
